hopobject.body: How much is a First Class stamp? duroil review Children of involved parents perform better in school than students whose parents are not involved. Parents demonstrate what is important to them by how they spend their time. It takes sacrifice. I give parents of students in my school two recommendations: 1. Spend an hour a night with your child. Read with them, have them read to. 2. No television or limited meaningful television time Monday-Thursday.
